race.comment: EFFIE'S JOY (4) finally got the maiden victory out of the way at Beaudesert last start and will have taken some confidence from that breakthrough win. Gets 3kg off with the claim and should get a cosy run in transit from gate two. Well placed to feature again. NEOCLASSICISM (1) loves it here on the Poly with two wins and ten placings from 18 spins. Another to get some weight off and ready to peak now third-up. Don't dismiss lightly. THE WELLIAN (2) goes well for hoop Hellyer who has two wins and three placings from ten steers. In the mix. HAYAKU (5) next in line. Mixed campaign last season but still netted two wins.
